Open thread channel opened
ESP can communicate through the channel with itself for now

commands inside powershell after the flash we get the OpenThread console
ot help /we can get all the commands

ot state /to check what state our channel is currently in
ot  thread start /we start the channel, this first might change the state from disabled -> detached but after a bit of waiting it should run and start fully,
wait till you get the state into "Leader", it shows in the terminal while running but if you want a quick check just run "ot state"

ot ipaddr /we get all the addresses we have, we use the first one IPv6

we can setup a port after that
ot udp open/ opens the port
ot udp bind :: 1111 / we can set the ports "name" channel with whatever 4 digits it doesnt have to be 1111 it can be custom

ot udp send (copy the ipv6 address that we mentioned earlier here) (custom port)1111 "Custom message"
